  "title": "RideableRavagers",
  "description": "This mod allows you to breed Ravagers with steak. Beware, they won't like you even if you feed them.",
  "body": "<center>\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uOay7qH.png\" width=\"230\" height=\"92\" alt=\"RideableRavagers\" title =\"RideableRavagers\">\n</center>\n\nThis was a request by FairyFlorra and I found the idea interesting, so here is the mod now for everyone.\n\nThis mod allows you to breed Ravagers with steak. Beware, they won't like you even if you feed them.\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/s_N3ovGf13g\" title=\"Breeding Ravagers\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\nIt is possible to lead baby ravagers as well as adult Ravagers\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/xCn2bmItGTM\" title=\"Lead Ravagers\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/F0EBSs5-XtA\" title=\"Lead Ravagers\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\nThe offspring can be tamed by feeding it more steak, if you don't feed it steak it will grow up to an untamed Ravager.\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/PfsTMrZRkEk\" title=\"Tame baby Ravagers\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\nOnce a tamed ravager grow's up you can attach a saddle to it by right clicking it with a saddle.\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/EbkobrlroGE\" title=\"Attach a saddle to a Ravager\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/vXAqpKguH_A\" title=\"Ride the Ravager\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\nYou can also make Ravagers spawn in Savannah biomes through the config menu.\n\n\nThe Fabric version needs FabricAPI.\n\nForge does not need any extra dependencies.\n\nFor the config the midnight library is used.",
